title: Young conservatives send mixed messages on Trump at MAGA gathering
description: Some attendees are talking about the former president more as a historical figure than the GOP's future presidential nominee.

title: Wine tasting in Napa and a staff revolt: How a progressive powerhouse went kaput
description: Founded after the 2004 Howard Dean presidential campaign, Democracy for America was felled by poor fundraising and what many former employees described as shoddy management.
